title: North Korea Launches Suspected Ballistic Missile Off Its East Coast, South Korea Says
sub_head: It marks Pyongyang’s seventh weapons launch this month—more than it had conducted all of last year
body:
SEOUL—North Korea’s flurry of January weapons tests continued on Sunday, as the Kim Jong Un regime launched a suspected ballistic missile off its east coast, South Korea’s military said.
It marks Pyongyang’s seventh weapons launch this month—more than it had conducted all of last year. The regime’s testing pace has never been this high.
